# Pillar ‚Äî Reliability

*Meet your uptime & recovery targets.*

## Checklist

- **Across AZs** ‚Äî ASG spans AZs, RDS/ElastiCache Multi-AZ, ALB cross-zone
- **Stateless compute** ‚Äî sessions‚ÜíElastiCache, files‚ÜíS3, secrets‚ÜíSecrets Mgr; any instance replaceable
- **Auto-recovery** ‚Äî ASG self-heal, ALB health checks, EC2 Auto Recovery, ECS reschedule
- **Service quotas** ‚Äî raise *before* you hit them; alarm on usage
- **DR chosen & tested** ‚Äî the four shapes, **quarterly drills**
- **Backpressure** ‚Äî SQS buffers, backoff + jitter, idempotent retries

## Principles

Auto-recover ¬∑ **test recovery** ¬∑ scale horizontally ¬∑ stop guessing capacity ¬∑ automate change

**Model:** *assume everything fails, make failure a non-event.* **Cue:** survive AZ outage / no SPOF / meet RTO ‚Üí this pillar.
